{"tid":1638560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【鼓勵篤灰】重推WeChat、Line、電郵等熱線","createTime":"2019-10-08T10:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T15:05:04.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"036eb716d5628cd87a6db448c6b35dfc42922f69","tid":1638560,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:54:20.000Z","msg":"警方上月曾推出十條WhatsApp「反暴力報料熱線」，惟被母公司facebook刪除熱線，警方仍隨即停用。至今日（10月8日），警方再度推出「更新版」，新增一個非緊急熱線號碼+852 5333 3103，適用於WeChat 、 Line、 SMS，市民亦可以使用熱線電郵，讓市民向警方提交情報，協助預防及偵查罪案。資訊系統部高級警司陳志勇指出，市民十分渴望社會恢復應有秩序，警方在不同渠道收到市民要求有一個非緊急熱線以提供資料，故重推熱線，並指上述三平台為市民常用平台。至於WhatsApp因該公司不同意，故警方今次未有使用。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/383570/警方記者會-重推wechat-line-電郵等熱線-whatsapp拒警使用</code></pre>"},{"pid":"414b59e2d3b37f9d7870586e9cfb9ce0eb08490e","tid":1638560,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"bestgore<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fcc9b6e616699a961dc91f99f76944e949533f","tid":1638560,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:55:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba7a45cf459d5b9e1eb5586cfbcacfef75e11807","tid":1638560,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T10:55:32.000Z","msg":"「香港警察反暴力報料熱線更新版」不聽任何來電<br />\n<br />\n根據警察網頁，新熱線號碼適用於WeChat 、 Line、 SMS，市民亦可選擇新熱線電郵 hotline@police.gov.hk。網頁指，近日示威活動暴力不斷升級，警方在與不同社交媒體溝通及聆聽社會各界人士意見後，決定更新反暴力報料熱線。"},{"pid":"64067b7a27eb47deff458b4c86e16ed5178ffce1","tid":1638560,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aac8538c929198d781bd240773a6be5523fbf1be","tid":1638560,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:13:04.000Z","msg":"藍屍準備好俾篤未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9d94a75505552409fb8fa33441994a8b6b58dc","tid":1638560,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"即係Line 同意了？"},{"pid":"baa4a6347d36ad136db5c620e11f0b57a30a14fa","tid":1638560,"uid":162822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea9d94a75505552409fb8fa33441994a8b6b58dc","tid":1638560,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:15:56.000Z","msg":"即係Line 同意了？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T11:18:15.000Z","msg":"Line果個好似5係官方帳號，係個人帳號<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63bb73dd95946bab8fb7900e596c9c0b187c01dc","tid":1638560,"uid":149383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:23:20.000Z","msg":"入去wechat講下8964先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b09c12e77f0c4c139697bec51fd3a6f3a8ba427","tid":1638560,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:25:07.000Z","msg":"Wechat亂咁篤灰當唔當虛報嫁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5fe8a26a8cd0b589255f8db70fd1b1ceac7523","tid":1638560,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gq1AbHO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgq1AbHO.jpg&h=03632d67&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}